metadata.name: Cosmos Access NFT
metadata.description: This NFT allows you to redeem for an e-ticket to Hypeworld 2022. The first-ever Music Festival NFT Collection in Singapore, and the first piece of the HYPEWORLD NFT collection. Join us on a journey with infinite possibilities. Benefits of holding this Cosmos Access NFT includes a 1x HYPEWORLD 2022 2-Day VIP pass, priority queues at the festival, access to an exclusive VIP area viewing experience and more! Join us on discord for the latest updates on the perks.
